-- PDVSA Is Confident on Pernambuco Refinery Project, Ramirez Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2012-01-24T21:30:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/pdvsa-is-confident-on-pernambuco-refinery-project-ramirez-says.html
Petroleos de Venezuela SA will
“surely” enter into the Pernambuco refinery project along with
 Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4) , company president  Rafael Ramirez  told
reporters today.  PDVSA is waiting for Brazilian banks to verify loan
guarantees provided by the Venezuelan state-oil company
including $1.5 billion of cash, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
